442">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19843746/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Automated+measurement+of+colorectal+polyp+height+at+CT+colonography%3A+hyperplastic+polyps+are+flatter+than+adenomatous+polyps&amp;author=RM+Summers&amp;author=J+Liu&amp;author=J+Yao&amp;author=L+Brown&amp;author=JR+Choi&amp;author=PJ+Pickhardt&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=1305-1310&amp;doi=10.2214%2FAJR.09.2442&amp;pmid=19843746">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">11.</div><div id="r11" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Torlakovic E, Skovlund E, Snover DC, Torlakovic G, Nesland JM. Morphologic reappraisal of serrated colorectal polyps. <em>Am J Surg Pathol</em> 2003;27(1):65–81.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/00000478-200301000-00008">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12502929/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Morphologic+reappraisal+of+serrated+colorectal+polyps&amp;author=E+Torlakovic&amp;author=E+Skovlund&amp;author=DC+Snover&amp;author=G+Torlakovic&amp;author=JM+Nesland&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;journal=Am+J+Surg+Pathol&amp;pages=65-81&amp;doi=10.1097%2F00000478-200301000-00008&amp;pmid=12502929">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Longacre TA, Fenoglio-Preiser CM. Mixed hyperplastic adenomatous polyps/serrated adenomas: a distinct form of colorectal neoplasia. <em>Am J Surg Pathol</em> 1990;14(6):524–537.</div><div class="external-links"><di